      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe the condition of this beauty\u2014it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've pampered this car since day one, and it shows in every single detail. It\u2019s super clean, runs like a dream, and is just waiting for someone who will love it as much as I have. If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin!",
