    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true time-capsule vehicle in showroom condition. The exterior features original factory paint with a deep, glass-like luster, free of any stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the alloy wheels are completely devoid of curb rash. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All electronics, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, function with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and maintained strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule. The engine bay is spotless, showing no signs of fluid leaks or aging. This vehicle drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line\u2014tight, quiet, and powerful. It is a preserved masterpiece ready for a discerning collector.",
